descriptionHtml:
Adds a new feathered guardian wings to real flying mod if you are bored of the scaly dragon wings u can use this mod 

Requires real flying mod by Anton0028 real flying mod to work 
controls are the same as real flying

INSTALLATION (use NMM do not manually install)

step 1 download and install real flying
step 2 run fnis
step 3 download and install this mod
step 4 run fnis again
step 5 enjoy
author: Anton0028
